## WHEN CURSOR SUGGESTS CODE

- Always suggest the async version of database/API calls
- Always include error handling
- Always add the metadata filters when writing Qdrant queries
- Always stream LLM responses — never wait for full completion
- When writing RAG code, always include the citation extraction logic
- Prefer LangChain abstractions over raw OpenAI calls
- When writing frontend fetch calls, always handle loading + error states

