## COMMON MISTAKES TO AVOID

1. Do NOT use synchronous SQLAlchemy — always async
2. Do NOT forget course_id filter in Qdrant queries — this causes cross-course data leakage
3. Do NOT buffer the full LLM response — always stream
4. Do NOT store API keys in code — always .env
5. Do NOT use the Pages Router in Next.js — App Router only
6. Do NOT skip Pydantic validation on incoming requests
7. Do NOT mix LlamaIndex and LangChain retrieval — use LlamaIndex for ingestion, LangChain for retrieval/generation
